<h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">A World-Class Research Experience </h2>
<p class="mb-4 text-xl">Since its founding in 1848, the University of Wisconsin&ndash;Madison has been a catalyst for the extraordinary. UW&ndash;Madison has more than $1.52 billion in annual research spending, a figure that puts us among the top 10 in the nation among universities for volume of research. We are distinct from other institutions due to our significant breadth of disciplines and cross-campus research collaborations. We invest in next-generation thought leaders and cutting-edge research infrastructure which together form an enterprise that benefits Wisconsin, the nation, and the world.  </p>

